ROME, Feb. 18 (Reuters)-- Two Christian Democrat Senators, Adone Zoli and Giuseppe Medici, have been chosen by Premier Antonio Segni to fill the vacant posts of Budget Minister and Minister of the Treasury, it was learned here tonight. View Full Article in Timesmachine Â»
